using (SqlConnection connection = new SqlConnection(connectionString))\n{\n    SqlDataAdapter adapter = new SqlDataAdapter("SELECT * FROM MyTable", connection);\n    SqlCommandBuilder builder = new SqlCommandBuilder(adapter);\n\n    DataSet dataSet = new DataSet();\n    adapter.Fill(dataSet, "MyTable");\n    \n    // Modify data in the dataset\n    foreach (var record in records)\n    {\n        DataRow row = dataSet.Tables["MyTable"].Rows.Find(record.ID);\n        if (row != null)\n        {\n            row["Column1"] = record.Value;\n        }\n    }\n\n    // Send changes back to database\n    using (new SqlCommandBuilder(adapter))\n    {\n        adapter.Update(dataSet, "MyTable");\n    }\n}